{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"instancetype"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"cameraLookingAtCenterCoordinate:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"centerCoordinate"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"altitude:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"CLLocationDistance","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@CLLocationDistance"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"altitude"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"pitch:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@CGFloat","text":"CGFloat"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"pitch"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"heading:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@CLLocationDirection","text":"CLLocationDirection","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"heading","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The geographic coordinate on which the map should be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"centered.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"centerCoordinate"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The altitude (measured in meters) above the map at which the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"camera should be situated. The altitude may be less than the distance from"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the camera’s viewpoint to the camera’s focus point."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"altitude"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The viewing angle of the camera, measured in degrees. A value of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0"},{"type":"text","text":" results in a camera pointed straight down at the map. Angles greater"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"than "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0"},{"type":"text","text":" result in a camera angled toward the horizon."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"pitch"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The camera’s heading, measured in degrees clockwise from true"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"north. A value of "},{"code":"0","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" means that the top edge of the map view corresponds to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"true north. The value "},{"code":"90","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" means the top of the map is pointing due east."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The value "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"180"},{"type":"text","text":" means the top of the map points due south, and so on."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"heading"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapCamera"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapcamera\/cameralookingatcentercoordinate:altitude:pitch:heading:"]}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"cameraLookingAtCenterCoordinate:altitude:pitch:heading:"}],"symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"cameraLookingAtCenterCoordinate:altitude:pitch:heading:"}],"title":"cameraLookingAtCenterCoordinate:altitude:pitch:heading:","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapCamera(cm)cameraLookingAtCenterCoordinate:altitude:pitch:heading:","roleHeading":"Type Method","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/M